Really kind lady who just wants you to be a competent dissertation writer. I had 70's in french in highschool and got an A in this class. You merely need to put in some effort and you'll be rewarded... Also, she takes class participation into consideration and adds substantial marks to your final grade if you don't skip the group presentations

Le cour en soit est plate, mais elle parle bien francais, pas fort, mais bien. Elle prend les presence, mais elle est toujours gentille et calme. Tres bonne enseignante si on prend en consideration le contenu morbide du cours

This prof is extremely boring. The subject of the class is bad enough, but the prof makes it worse. She speaks very softly, yet refuses to use a microphone. No grammatical rules are ever explained. This class is useless and is there only to lower your GPA. Expect to hear "Silence s'il vous plait!" quite often. Attendance is also mandatory.

The class was indeed boring but she is a good professor. She knows her subject really well and is always happy to help. Maybe a bit too brief about the report as such, which counts for 50 %.Might be useful to know that attendance in her class is mandatory.
